      <title>印度通胀在民意调查前降至10个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/india-inflation-cools-in-march-on-decline-in-food-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于食品和燃料价格下跌，印度 3 月份零售通胀降至 10 个月低点，尽管即将到来的热浪可能会损害农作物并有可能推高价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/india-inflation-cools-in-march-on-decline-in-food-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>矿石短缺满足需求复苏，铜价持续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lme-copper-rises-to-highest-since-june-2022-as-outlook-brightens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价继续上涨，触及 2022 年 6 月以来的最高水平，因为投资者押注减少的矿石供应将难以跟上全球不断增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lme-copper-rises-to-highest-since-june-2022-as-outlook-brightens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:14:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
